Symbol.Script_2D:
b=rad+rad_abst
pen gs_cont_pen set fill gs_fill_type
set line_type lin_typ
poly2_b 5, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -a/2, -b/2, 1, -a/2, b/2, 1, a/2, b/2, 1, a/2, -b/2, 1, -a/2, -b/2, -1
set line_type lin_kont
poly2_b 5, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, a/2, b/2, 1, a/2, b/2+sp, 1, -a/2, b/2+sp, 1, -a/2, b/2, 1, a/2, b/2, -1
Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iContVolumeType VOLUMETYPE_500L = 1 VOLUMETYPE_660L = 2 VOLUMETYPE_770L = 3 VOLUMETYPE_1000L = 4 VOLUMETYPE_1100L = 5
if iContVolumeType = VOLUMETYPE_500L then parameters a=1.36 parameters b=0.65 parameters zzyzx=1.14 parameters h2=1.04 parameters roll=0.87 parameters rad=0.38 endif
if iContVolumeType = VOLUMETYPE_660L then parameters a=1.36 parameters b=0.77 parameters zzyzx=1.18 parameters h2=1.10 parameters roll=0.87 parameters rad=0.49 endif
if iContVolumeType = VOLUMETYPE_770L then parameters a=1.36 parameters b=0.77 parameters zzyzx=1.33 parameters h2=1.26 parameters roll=0.87 parameters rad=0.49 endif
if iContVolumeType = VOLUMETYPE_1000L then parameters a=1.36 parameters b=1.08 parameters zzyzx=1.32 parameters h2=1.20 parameters roll=0.88 parameters rad=0.75 endif
if iContVolumeType = VOLUMETYPE_1100L then parameters a=1.36 parameters b=1.08 parameters zzyzx=1.47 parameters h2=1.20 parameters roll=0.88 parameters rad=0.75 endif
lock "a", "b", "zzyzx", "h2", "roll", "rad"
v=0.01 !thickness of material rad_abst=0.1 !differense between roll axes and depth roll_h=0.20 !height of roll-top sp=B-rad-rad_abst !space for cover dh=zzyzx-h2
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "iContVolumeType" VOLUMETYPE_500L, `500 л`, VOLUMETYPE_660L, `660 л`, VOLUMETYPE_770L, `770 л`, VOLUMETYPE_1000L, `1000 л`, VOLUMETYPE_1100L, `1100 л`
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.`
